text: Fleet Admiral Feliks Nikolayevich Gromov (; August 29, 1937 - January 22, 2021) was a Russian admiral. He was the Commander-in-Chief of the Russian Navy from 1992 to 1997. Gromov was born in Vladivostok, Soviet Union. Gromov died on January 22, 2021 at the age of 83.Умер экс-главком ВМФ России Феликс Громов ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Russian military people Category:People from Vladivostok
